data.description: Opportunity awaits in the heart of Roswell! This light, bright and airy traditional two story home is in an unbeatable location. Quick access to shopping, dining, parks, and more. The brand-new front door welcomes you in to this freshly painted home offering an open floor plan on the main level with a large dining room, separate living room, and eat-in kitchen overlooking the family room all with hardwoods. Upstairs are three secondary bedrooms, full bath, and an oversized primary suite. The primary suite is a true retreat with a large office featuring built-in bookshelves and French doors, a walk-in closet, and a generously sized bath. Newer HVAC systems, hot water heater and garage doors with wifi enabled quiet openers. The fenced backyard features a play area, fire pit, paver patio and plenty of areas for gardens. Spacious garage with plenty of storage. Conveniently located near area private schools including Fellowship Christian, Queen of Angels, and Blessed Trinity as well as highly-regarded Crabapple Middle and Roswell High. Close proximity to Roswell Area Park and Downtown Roswell/Historic Canton Street area. Zoned for award-winning Mountain Park Elementary! Don't miss out on this adorable Roswell home!
